# Dev images mount the repo at runtime (compose `volumes: ..:/workspace`) and COPY
# nothing at build time, so node_modules and build artifacts must stay out of the
# build context — scanning them is slow and trips over root-owned cache files
# (e.g. apps/web/node_modules/.tmp) the host user cannot read.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.output
**/.nuxt
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/storybook-static
**/.dart_tool
apps/mobile/build
apps/mobile/ios
apps/mobile/android

# Local SQLite dev DB (provisioned in-container by `prisma migrate deploy`)
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal

# VCS + misc
.git
**/*.log
